I"<p><strong>Huge giant (frost giant), chaotic evil</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 15 (patchwork armor)</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 189 (14d12+98)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 40 ft.</p>

